{"tid":397344,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黃乃共：中大有開明的良好傳統，不會追究這些事","createTime":"2017-09-12T11:55:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-12T15:46:31.000Z","uid":5195,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"be1ea08d9128710e0a04aa0a76813d1b4597d015","tid":397344,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T11:55:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://eastweek.my-magazine.me/main/49613\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Feastweek.my-magazine.me%2Fmain%2F49613&d=8bPRNTdYQG2t6jThgla6w57TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=bafd0841\" target=\"_blank\">http://eastweek.my-magazine.me/main/49613</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eastweek.com.hk/article_multimedia/49613/1_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eastweek.com.hk%2Farticle_multimedia%2F49613%2F1_n.jpg&h=9e107c81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n黃乃正設法加碼籌二千萬元，卻遇上不利時勢，「院長負責籌款，好慘，左中右人士都是我的籌款對象，有人會單單打打，說『學生住帳幕得啦，住甚麼宿舍！』佔領運動後，好大代溝。」黃乃正六九年入讀中大，主修化學，典型書獃子，整天待在實驗室，但七十年代中文運動和保釣運動他都有參加罷課、維園集會。他認為：「<span style=\"color: red;\">學生不搞事，就沒有向上動力。老人家看不順眼後生仔，代代如是。</span>」<br />\n<br />\n佔領運動期間，新亞水塔垂掛一幅「我要真普選」標語，黃乃正和沈祖堯都沒過問，「（中大校董會主席）鄭海泉年輕時一樣激，一樣瞓街抗議，<span style=\"color: red;\">中大有開明的良好傳統，不會追究這些事</span>。」"},{"pid":"7adb743439e885ae835e327eea6f41613f424144","tid":397344,"uid":22858,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T11:56:38.000Z","msg":"但會敏感 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e4b019102a08fd3f5e57201090d588f076b2b14","tid":397344,"uid":117837,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T11:59:57.000Z","msg":"呢啲真係典型廢老懶開明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好地地就話好欣賞年輕人乜乜柒柒<br />\n但一郁到佢嘅利益就即刻屌鳩你廢青"},{"pid":"600dad7e578d1418f600c41f590654e6687085c5","tid":397344,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T12:04:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>但會敏感 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f79cb1141c9ae7a5e321d32c81aaa13f661573a","tid":397344,"uid":130513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T12:16:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7707950d0d88e7ee1757ec48025a01d59630e383","tid":397344,"uid":28279,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T12:20:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 此一時彼一時"},{"pid":"a2d96169a935faaf22cb68c67713bf2bc2b9ac12","tid":397344,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T12:28:42.000Z","msg":"精神分裂！"},{"pid":"ac51e0e55b907925dd6a31a2c54cf83041ae339f","tid":397344,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T12:29:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/12/202923_160fa5ce6d0cd81ffeba811bc3f2b074.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F12%2F202923_160fa5ce6d0cd81ffeba811bc3f2b074.jpg&h=06093ef1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e5029e44701f3df90d2e9ca90683794c0e79690a","tid":397344,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T15:46:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}